</TARGET_SUMMARY_TOKENS>

Allowed actions:
{% if selective_store_enabled %}
- skip: do not store this scope because it adds no useful durable continuity memory.
- append: store this scope under the given topic heading. If the heading already
  exists, a later step will add the note there; otherwise a new heading is
  created.
{% else %}
- append: store this scope under the given topic heading. If the heading already
  exists, a later step will add the note there; otherwise a new heading is
  created.
{% endif %}

Return JSON with this shape:
{
  "action": "{% if selective_store_enabled %}skip{% else %}append{% endif %}",
  "section_title": "Source-side section/topic title, not a target-language term mapping",
  "reason": "Short reason for skipping or storing. If storing, state the new durable future dependency."
}
